<BaseLayout
  title="Technical Debt: When to Pay It Down vs. When to Just Live With It | Uncle Data"
  description="PyCon Lithuania 2026 keynote. A framework for deciding when technical debt is worth fixing, with real war stories."
>

  <div class="pt-12 pb-4">
